{"tid":1831806,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【急推！幫還柙手足問！】監房手足，你問我答","createTime":"2020-01-20T16:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T03:45:31.000Z","uid":270466,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c92ecb58688d2611adab03283509dbf5f8c2ddea","tid":1831806,"uid":270466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"事緣係上次我喺度share咗篇喺蘋果嘅公開信 (寫信嗰個手足自稱做stories behind the prison，後來先知原來佢係我個friend個friend)︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200108/PVXOYKQB5ERAKJJ63AUGDX4BQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200108%2FPVXOYKQB5ERAKJJ63AUGDX4BQY%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV91yVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=0d03c13c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200108%2FPVXOYKQB5ERAKJJ63AUGDX4BQY%2F&h=aad0894b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200108/PVXOYKQB5ERAKJJ63AUGDX4BQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n佢最近再寫信出嚟話想借連登acc出post，因為想繼續寫公開信，同大家講吓監房小故事，又或者係想大家傾下出面嘅嘢，唔想因為還柙而中斷咗同外界嘅聯繫，所以想公開求問大家寫咩題材。信嘅內容如下 (我都會將呢個連登post俾埋張超雄議辦，希望工作人員會幫手出post)︰<br />\n<br />\n「巴絲們你地好，我係之前寫咗好長公開信果個手足<br />\n見到你哋嘅留言真係又開心又滾動 (sticker︰連狗喊喊)<br />\n不過叫我兄弟真係好好笑<br />\n<br />\n喺度還柙就嚟悶死我啦，想寫吓啲監房小故事俾大家睇呀<br />\n但因為喺度坐咗一段時間，同出面社會有些少脫節<br />\n又驚寫完啲嘢出嚟唔好睇，或者你哋唔中意睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以想收集下大家意見<br />\n你哋有咩想知想八卦就留言啦</span></span><br />\n輕鬆 or 沉重嘅主題我都會分享 (sticker︰連豬打鼓x3)<br />\n我會努力寫同努力生活，唔使擔心<br />\n<br />\n同埋見有巴絲問想寄信俾我<br />\n可以寄去張超雄議辦 (立法會道一號立法會綜合大樓1017室張超雄議員辦事處)<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n感性還感性，平日我都係上lecture果陣碌吹水台同cc台嘅災嚟<br />\n想講好掛住6月之前嘅連登<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有分化post，只有分手post嘅連登</span></span> (sticker︰腦魔喊喊)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我同其他拋緊，坐緊嘅手足都唔會放棄<br />\n你哋都唔可以！</span></span><br />\n我哋唔喺度嘅日子你哋要努力啦<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望有朝一日我坐完監出嚟仲可以見到你哋</span></span><br />\n你哋要保重呀知唔知」"},{"pid":"48de39645649c2d87d2d6780faa18186e5ec5367","tid":1831806,"uid":266149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b0b1885cae3d7f6766fb8316e4bd8389180e0c","tid":1831806,"uid":270466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTkoTg1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTkoTg1.jpg&h=d629b424&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e26d5fb7940f28edc6a7e2802e3daad19e0bfe93","tid":1831806,"uid":89591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T20:11:12.000Z","msg":"保重唨咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cf18716a84ab57ea51458b546219247a825dfd","tid":1831806,"uid":89591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e26d5fb7940f28edc6a7e2802e3daad19e0bfe93","tid":1831806,"uid":89591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T20:11:12.000Z","msg":"保重唨咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T20:11:47.000Z","msg":"保重「啊」咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0145351fb4cd189f57018c7bfd9ceb9bc5cb99d2","tid":1831806,"uid":132551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9454add04257fd282f17c0a9105c827144e12f4a","tid":1831806,"uid":225652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:45:31.000Z"